objects.name: Dialogue

variables.name: Intro
variables.value: Welcome to General Chemistry! To navigate the classroom, use W to jump, A and D to walk, and S to fall through platforms.

variables.name: Tutorial2
variables.value: Congratulations on making it through your first week! To pass the class, you'll need to make it to Week 10, all the way up here.

variables.name: Tutorial3
variables.value: Can't make a jump? Use W to climb the stairs instead.

variables.name: Tutorial4
variables.value: Sometimes you'll come across a difficult concept. Don't get caught off guard, or you might have to review the previous weeks.

variables.name: Victory
variables.value: Congratulations, and good luck on the rest of your journey through college!
